%BA%A7n-T%E1%BB%B1-Kh%C3%A1nh/Th%E1%BB%89nh-%C4%91%E1%BA%BF-ph%E1%BA%A3n-gi%C3%A1-kinh-s%C6%B0/poem-ljWYlNa1by48BdM-GbgSbQ">Thỉnh đế phản giá kinh sư - 請帝返駕京師</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-T%E1%BB%B1-Kh%C3%A1nh/author-vn-49B8xHWgiPat6tqvDUw">Trần Tự Khánh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Tr%C3%A1ng-du/poem-dLYEgwcQ7IbIIq24Mpcddw">Tráng du - 壯遊</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Linh/T%E1%BB%ADu-%C4%91%E1%BB%A9c-t%E1%BB%A5ng/poem-J13HP-vW93XWQ7-28U2Z0A">Tửu đức tụng - 酒德頌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Linh/author-hkIbirWYM3zvfGsJ_u2tHQ">Lưu Linh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/V%C4%83n-h%E1%BA%A3i-%C4%91%C3%A0o-thanh/poem-SY2WPjNEFVqHEp46v0OCQA">Văn hải đào thanh - 聞海濤聲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br></div>	</div>
